  "detailed_description": "<strong>Ascending Madness</strong> is a hardcore, psychedelic, twinstick shooter with a dark trippy vibe and fast fluid combat.<br><br>Take on the role of a merciless bounty hunter as he encounters increasing madness while on a mission.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/750240/extras/08924432355ffd0bf619e3abd01e8cf1.avif?t=1567871991\" width=500 height=83 /></span><br><br><strong>Assassinate a renegade scientist and her group of devout followers who appear to have gone completely insane.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/750240/extras/c3f41267ec1395997d54d45cdfd73707.avif?t=1567871991\" width=500 height=83 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast Combat Across Diverse Arenas<br></li><li><strong>Bosses!</strong><br></li><li>Intense Futuristic Weaponry, like the <strong>'Flame Sword'</strong>, <strong>'Sniper Laser'</strong>, and <strong>'Pulverizer'</strong><br></li><li>Waves of <strong>Bizarre Monstrosities</strong><br></li><li>Interesting <strong>Rune Upgrades</strong> for your Battlecraft<br></li><li>Story Mode Involving the Psychedelic, the Spiritual, and the Surreal<br></li><li>Challenge Mode to Compete for High Scores<br></li><li>Colorful and Gritty Art Style<br></li><li>The Meaning of Life</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Ascending Madness</strong> is a hardcore, psychedelic, twinstick shooter with a dark trippy vibe and fast fluid combat.<br><br>Take on the role of a merciless bounty hunter as he encounters increasing madness while on a mission.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/750240/extras/08924432355ffd0bf619e3abd01e8cf1.avif?t=1567871991\" width=500 height=83 /></span><br><br><strong>Assassinate a renegade scientist and her group of devout followers who appear to have gone completely insane.</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/750240/extras/c3f41267ec1395997d54d45cdfd73707.avif?t=1567871991\" width=500 height=83 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast Combat Across Diverse Arenas<br></li><li><strong>Bosses!</strong><br></li><li>Intense Futuristic Weaponry, like the <strong>'Flame Sword'</strong>, <strong>'Sniper Laser'</strong>, and <strong>'Pulverizer'</strong><br></li><li>Waves of <strong>Bizarre Monstrosities</strong><br></li><li>Interesting <strong>Rune Upgrades</strong> for your Battlecraft<br></li><li>Story Mode Involving the Psychedelic, the Spiritual, and the Surreal<br></li><li>Challenge Mode to Compete for High Scores<br></li><li>Colorful and Gritty Art Style<br></li><li>The Meaning of Life</li></ul>",
